<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport"
          content="width=device-width, user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
<form method="get" action="/script/{{selectScriptPaper.script_id}}/updatescriptpaper">
    <input name="script_id" type="hidden" value="{{selectScriptPaper.script_id}}"/>

<table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1">
    <tr>
        <td>씬 번호(자동입력 필요)<input name="scene_id" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.scene_id}}" ></td>
        <td>영상 제목<input name="video_name" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.video_name}}" ></td>
        <td>촬영날짜<input name="video_date" type="date" value="{{selectScriptPaper.video_date}}" ></td>
        <td>촬영시작시간<input name="video_time" type="date" value="{{selectScriptPaper.video_time}}" ></td>
        <td>촬영종료시간<input name="video_end_time" type="date" value="{{selectScriptPaper.video_end_time}}" ></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>액션 이미지 첨부파일 <input name="action_image" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.action_image}}" /></td>
        <td>액션 내용 <input name="action_content" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.action_content}}" /></td>
        <td>카메라포지션 첨부파일 <input name="position_image" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.position_image}}" /></td>
        <td>콘티 <input name="conti" type="text" value="{{selectScriptPaper.conti}}" /></td>
    </tr>
</table>
    <input type="submit" value="수정"/>
</form>
<a href="/script/scriptpaper">취소</a>
<br/>현재까지 버그<br/>
</body>
</html>